<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Home</title>
    <%- include("./partials/head") %>
  </head>
  <body>
    <%- include("./partials/navBar") %>
    <div class="container">
      <h1 class="display-4 fw-bold text-primary text-center my-3">
        Hamelberg Group
      </h1>
      <p class="lead text-muted text-center m-2" style="font-size: 1.75rem">
        Exploring Cell Signaling at the Atomic Level
      </p>
      <!-- Bootstrap Grid for Image + Text -->
      <div class="row align-items-center my-4"> 
        <div class="col text-center">
          <img
            src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/gh/AaradhyaNagar/Hamelberg_Public_Assets/images/jpcb_cover.jpg"
            class="img-fluid rounded shadow-lg"
            style="max-height: 500px"
            alt="Research Cover"
          />
        </div>
        <div class="col" style="font-size: 1.25rem">
          <p class="content" style="line-height: 1.8;">
            Our research delves into the intricate world of subcellular
            processes, leveraging advanced computational techniques to unravel
            the complexities of cell signaling. By simulating molecular
            interactions, we aim to decode the mechanisms that govern biological
            functions at an atomic scale.
          </p>

          <p class="content" style="line-height: 1.8">
            Disruptions in these pathways can lead to severe conditions such as
            cancer and other diseases. Through a fusion of statistical
            mechanics, quantum chemistry, and cutting-edge simulations, we
            explore the fundamental principles—like allostery—that drive
            cellular behavior, complementing experimental research with deep
            theoretical insights.
          </p>

          <p class="content text-primary fw-semibold" style="line-height: 1.8">
            Our mission is to bridge the gap between computation and biology,
            transforming complex molecular interactions into actionable
            scientific discoveries.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="my-5">
        <hr
          class="w-100 mx-auto border-primary opacity-100"
          style="height: 3px; border-radius: 5px"
        />
      </div>

      <h1 class="display-5 fw-bold text-center my-3" style="color: #1f75fe">
        Recent Selected Publications
      </h1>

      <div class="container">
        <ul class="list-group list-group-flush">
          <% if (locals.publications) { %> <% publications.slice(0,
          6).forEach(publication => { %>
          <li class="list-group-item px-0 py-3">
            <h5 class="fw-bold mb-1">
              <span>&#9702;</span>
              <%= publication.title %>
            </h5>
            <p class="mb-0 text-muted">
              <strong>Author(s):</strong> <%= publication.author %> |
              <strong>Year:</strong> <%= publication.year %> |
              <strong>Journal:</strong> <%= publication.journal %>
            </p>
            <a
              href="<%= publication.journal_link %>"
              target="_blank"
              class="text-decoration-none fw-semibold text-primary"
            >
              Read More →
            </a>
          </li>
          <% }) %> <% } %>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <%- include("./partials/footer") %> <%- include("./partials/script") %>
  </body>
</html>
